---
title: Sticky Glazed Chicken Breast and Chipotle Pilaf with Caramelised Onion, Peas and Soured Cream
description: This Sticky Glazed Chicken Breast and Chipotle Pilaf combines the Indian technique of pilaf, a sautéed rice dish, with Tex-Mex flavours. Chipotle is full of rich, smoky and fruity flavours with a kick from the chipotle chillies.
